description._content:
This is the main enclosed garden with the pond, because it is deep it needs to be gated,
On my tags I will put all the flowers that you see, because of the very bad rain storm we had yesterday the Glads are bending in the pebble path, more ready to bloom to the right in front of the roses, 
They are 5 different Waterlilies plus Water Hyacinths in the pond, next to the waterfall those Yellow flowers are are prickly pear cactus that come up every year even with our bad winter,
I will comment on all my contacts before I leave and will catch up on Tuesday,
Have a great Sunday everyone!
